name: 666 Masks
summary: How to survive despair and fear? Stir up your emotions. Look at the world in a new way. Get out of the maze of the catacombs by completing interesting quests. Collect all Masks and become alive again...

name: 66 Balls
summary:
"66 Balls" is mini physical game.
Shoot color balls to cups to get scores.
"66 Balls" has lots of tracks.Time is the key!
It looks like easy, but if you don't control the time, you can't be god!

name: 66 Bricks
summary:
Give you 66 bricks, build your own tower.
Physical version of Tetris, be arbitrary place bricks, build a variety of towers, challenge the patience and balance limits, see how high you can stack.
How to play: Move your finger left and right to adjust the position of the bricks, move your finger down brick drop quickly , tap the screen rotate bricks.

name: 666 Second Rule
summary: 666 Second Rule is an action game where you take a role of a tormented parent battling relentless insects. Utilize dark powers to fend off their disturbing attempts to crawl into the baby's head. Embrace the darkness within and prepare for an intense and gritty showdown.
Old-skool FPS gameplay with modern graphics and extra horror.
